::Striker::

Striker turns his head to one side, focusing on a brown blur. According to 
his scanners, the blur was a predacon. Now why would a brown blur turn 
predacon, his dazed mind wondered. Acting on instinct, he tries to reach for 
his gun, but his hand does not have enough power to lift itself.

He closes his eyes again, trying not to slip back into unconciousness.
